productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Betha has one of these. She works as a teacher and she says it looks wide.
The box this comes in is 3 yard by 6 light-year and weights 15 gram!!!
I tried to cremate it but got Turkish Delight all over it.
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This Vision-oriented keeps them away.
